Package: autometabR
Title: Comprehensive Metabolomics Data Analysis and Visualization
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Luiz", "Garcia", 
           email = "luiz.cardoso@ufpr.br", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9616-0927", affiliation = "UFPR"))
Description: Provides a suite of functions for metabolomics data analysis. 
    Supports raw data import, normalization, quality control, 
    and visualization, including heatmaps, PCA, UMAP, correlation matrices, 
    and Venn diagrams. Includes statistical testing such as t-tests, 
    Mann-Whitney U, and correlation, as well as dimensionality reduction 
    and biomarker discovery tools. Designed for ease of use and reproducible 
    workflows in metabolomics research.
